entries.journal_entry_description: Tuwezz Vol will test your hunting abilities by asking you to hunt ullers in Etyyy.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go to the Hracca Glade gate camp and speak with Tuwezz Vol. A waypoint for his location has been uploaded to your datapad.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Seek Tuwezz Vol at the Hracca Glade gate camp
entries.task01_waypoint_name: Tuwezz Vol at the Hracca Glade gate camp
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Some ullers in the area are spreading the disease they carry to other creatures. Hunt these diseased ullers and help reduce their numbers.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Tuwezz and let him know you've thinned the population of diseased ullers.
